ch offers,\\\" Cian said.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.324857737680855e-14, \"text\": \"Cian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Irish team is very strong and so to make Olympic selection having enough horsepower and being match-fit is so important.\\\"\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.941652844304578, \"rank\": 0.03572893952155122, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The plan is that both horses will be future rides for Sarah's daughter Keira.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"score\": 0.981999282627336, \"rank\": 0.01828709430008377, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more from Cian and Sarah      The Animals (Penalty Notices) Act has come into force, allowing local authorities to issue fines of up to \\u00a35,000 for animal welfare offences.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1138, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.324857737680855e-14, \"text\": \"Cian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Horse Welfare has welcomed the news, and said \\\"the notices will allow local authorities to take stron